#

Garlic Butter Shrimp and Pork Medley

$25
650 kcal

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-Free

Tags:

FrenchGourmetSeafoodComfort Food

Description

A rich and indulgent dish combining succulent shrimp and tender pork in a garlic butter sauce, served over a bed of creamy polenta.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • Garlic: 6 cloves, minced
  • Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Chicken broth: 1 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
